form.official-title: Providing for a correction in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 3979.

section.text: That in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 3979, the Clerk of the House of Representatives shall correct the title so as to read: An Act to authorize appropriations for fiscal year 2015 for military activities of the Department of Defense, for military construction, and for defense activities of the Department of Energy, to prescribe military personnel strengths for such fiscal year, and for other purposes..

attestation-group.attestation-date: Passed the House of Representatives December 4, 2014.
